{"name":{"entry":107,"name":"Al-Ma'un","meaning":"The Small kindnesses"},"verses":[{"arabic":" أَرَءَيْتَ ٱلَّذِى يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","translation":"Seest thou one who denies the Judgment (to come)?","transliteration":"Araayta allathee yukaththibu biddeen"},{"arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِى يَدُعُّ ٱلْيَتِيمَ","translation":"Then such is the (man) who repulses the orphan (with harshness),","transliteration":"Fathalika allathee yaduAAAAualyateem"},{"arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلْمِسْكِينِ","translation":"And encourages not the feeding of the indigent.","transliteration":"Wala yahuddu AAalataAAami almiskeen"},{"arabic":"فَوَيْلٌ لِّلْمُصَلِّينَ","translation":"So woe to the worshippers","transliteration":"Fawaylun lilmusalleen"},{"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمْ عَن صَلَاتِهِمْ سَاهُونَ","translation":"Who are neglectful of their prayers,","transliteration":"Allatheena hum AAan salatihimsahoon"},{"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمْ يُرَآءُونَ","translation":"Those who (want but) to be seen (of men),","transliteration":"Allatheena hum yuraoon"},{"arabic":"وَيَمْنَعُونَ ٱلْمَاعُونَ","translation":"But refuse (to supply) (even) neighbourly needs.","transliteration":"WayamnaAAoona almaAAoon"}]}